1 Index (All Urban Consumers, U.S. City Average for All Items), CPI-I, or its successor index, as
2 calculated by the U.S. Department of Labor for the 12-month period preceding the previous
3 September 1. Each adjusted minimum wage rate calculated shall be published on September 30
4 and take effect on the following January 1.
5 …."
6 SECTION 1.1.(c) This section is effective when this act becomes law.
