37 STATE EMPLOYEES' RETIREMENT SYSTEM, THE CONSOLIDATED JUDICIAL
38 RETIREMENT SYSTEM, THE LEGISLATIVE RETIREMENT SYSTEM, AND THE
39 LOCAL GOVERNMENTAL EMPLOYEES' RETIREMENT SYSTEM
40 SECTION 4.1.(a) G.S. 135-5 is amended by adding a new subsection to read:
41 "(aaaa) Effective July 1, 2025, the retirement allowance payable to, or on account of,
42 beneficiaries whose retirement commenced on or before July 1, 2024, is increased by three
43 percent (3%) of the allowance payable on June 1, 2024, in accordance with subsection (o) of this
44 section. Effective July 1, 2025, the retirement allowance payable to, or on account of,
45 beneficiaries whose retirement commenced after July 1, 2024, but before June 30, 2025, is
46 increased by a prorated amount of three percent (3%), as determined by the Board of Trustees
47 based upon the number of months that a retirement allowance was paid between July 1, 2024,
48 and June 30, 2025."
49 SECTION 4.1.(b) G.S. 135-65 is amended by adding a new subsection to read:
50 "(ll) Effective July 1, 2025, the retirement allowance payable to, or on account of,
51 beneficiaries whose retirement commenced on or before July 1, 2024, is increased by three
